| !Help2 for Fireworkz
|
If "<File$Type_FAF>"="" Then Error No browser found to display HTML help
|
RMEnsure SparkFS 1.36 If "<SparkFS$Dir>"="" Then Error SparkFS needs to be present to extract HTML help files
RMEnsure SparkFS 1.36 <SparkFS$Dir>.!Run -quit
RMEnsure SparkFS 1.36 Error SparkFS module 1.36 or later needs to be running to extract HTML help files
RMEnsure Zip 0.00 Error Zip module needs to be running to extract HTML help files
|
Set Fireworkz$HelpFile <Fireworkz$Dir>.Resource.HTMLHelp.html.index/htm
IfThere <Fireworkz$HelpFile> Then Else Set Fireworkz$HelpFile <Fireworkz$Dir>.^.HTMLHelp.html.index/htm
IfThere <Fireworkz$HelpFile> Then Filer_Run <Fireworkz$HelpFile> Else Error Fireworkz HTML help file not found
